Headline: According to Gran, the company has no plans to move all production to Russia, although that is where the company is growing.
For the last quarter of 2010, Basware expects its net sales to remain at the same level with the third quarter.
FINANCING OF ASPOCOMP'S GROWTH Aspocomp is aggressively pursuing its growth strategy by increasingly focusing on technologically more demanding HDI printed circuit boards PCBs.
